Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ruby | ruby-interpreter
Description: Easy printing to serial thermal ESCPOS printers
 Collection of methods that make printing of plain text and images
 to one or many serial thermal ESCPOS printers easy. Both USB and serial
 (RS232) printers are supported and detected automatically. Escper is
 useful for Ruby based Point of Sale systems that want to print receipts
 or tickets.